data.description: New High Efficiency Furnace And AC! New Water Heater! New Shingles And Exterior Paint In 2021! This 4-bed, 2-full bath home features a fully fenced back yard with shed and heated/insulated 2-stall garage! The master bedroom is huge and features a full/private master bath! NEW KITCHEN APPLIANCES, WASHER AND DRYER! Fantastic layout, flooring and condition! The dining room walks out to the deck and incredible yard! The upper level living room is spacious and the large windows bring in amazing natural light! The lower level family room offers ample space for recreation and leisure! This home is turn-key! Schedule your showing today!
